%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^MAGENTA%^Trickery Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Masters of mischief, those with the trickery domain relish the opportunity to confound their foes. The domain has a wide range of abilities, from concealing oneself to creating much confusion in one's enemies.

Clerics with the Trickery Domain gain the following benefits:
- +1 bonus to caster level when casting illusion sphere spells.
- Stealth as a class skill.

The trickery domain contains the following spells:

Alter Self, Displacement, Mass Invisibility, Screen, Timestop

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Callamir

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
